==Translingual==

===Noun===
''[[Gymnospermae]]''

# {{botany}} A [[botanical name]], not tied to any rank. [[Circumscription]] of the ''Gymnospermae'' is stable: it is the group of [[seed plants]], whose [[seed]]s are not enclosed in an [[ovary]]. The most important group of ''Gymnospermae'' are the [[conifers]] (''[[Coniferae]]'' or ''[[Coniferales]]'').

